<!Doctype Html>  
<Html>     
<Head>      
<Title>     
Add the Line using Html tags  
</Title>  
</Head>  
<Body>   
<hr size="8" width="100%" color="green">  
</Body>   
</Html>





<!Doctype Html>  
<Html>     
<Head>      
<Title>     
Add the Line using Internal CSS.   
</Title>  
<style>  
hr  
{  
width: 80%;  
height: 2px;  
background-color: pink;  
margin-bottom: 7px;  
margin-right: auto;  
margin-left: auto;  
margin-top: 9px;  
border-width: 4px;  
border-color: blue;  
}  
</style>  
</Head>  
<Body>   
This page helps you to understand how to add the line in Html document.  
<hr>  
And, this section helps you to understand how to add the line using the Internal Cascading Style Sheet.  
</Body>   
</Html>  
